<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 10px 0;
        background-color: #4caf50;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: white;
        background-color: #4caf50;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Tech Opp Academy!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>
          Dear {{firstName}},
        </p>
        <p>
          Thank you for joining <strong>Tech Opp Academy</strong>, a platform dedicated to empowering children in need through accessible learning opportunities.
        </p>
        <p>
          Your journey toward making a difference starts here. Please activate your account to explore our platform and support our mission of changing lives through education.
        </p>
        <a href="{{activationUrl}}" class="cta-button">Activate My Account</a>
        <p>
          If you did not sign up for this account, please ignore this email.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          Tech Opp Academy - Together, we build a brighter future.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
